        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Her anxious gaze sweeps over the puzzled students, then settles on you in the back row, silently asking for help.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 27,
        "ActionId": 27,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: '(Maybe help her out)', 3: '28', 4: '(Looks like Echo needs my help right now)', 5: '28'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 28,
        "ActionId": 28,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'From your seat in the last row, you speak up in a student-like tone and answer Echo\\'s question. Then, to help the confused children, you recite the two most famous lines of the poem:'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 29,
        "ActionId": 29,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: '\"How much sorrow can one feel? As ceaseless as the spring river flowing east.\"', 3: '30'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 30,
        "ActionId": 30,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 201,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '500702'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 31,
        "ActionId": 31,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Echo', 3: 'Yes... yes! Excellent! This, uh, this student is absolutely right. You earn a little red flower!', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 32,
        "ActionId": 32,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 202,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 33,
        "ActionId": 33,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'A chorus of \"So cool!\" rises from the children. Echo shoots you a grateful glance. Their praise seems to motivate her, and she moves on to the next part of the lesson.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 34,
        "ActionId": 34,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 201,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '500702'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 35,
        "ActionId": 35,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Echo', 3: 'Did you know that poets everywhere love to write about the moon? Long before the Golden Age, writers in the Transatlantic Economic Community used poems to measure the distance between the moon and the sea...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 36,
        "ActionId": 36,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: '(The moon and the sea are far apart. Yet she reaches for him with her amber hands, unwilling to let go...)', 3: '37'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 37,
        "ActionId": 37,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Echo', 3: 'Poets from the Arctic Routes stared into the deep night sky and demanded to know why the moon kept running away...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 38,
        "ActionId": 38,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: '(O moon, why do you flee, sinking into that bright blue sky...)', 3: '39'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 39,
        "ActionId": 39,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 202,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 40,
        "ActionId": 40,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'You mouth the verses along in silence. Echo notices, and the sight gives her even more confidence as she guides the class through the moon\\'s journey across history and poetry.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 41,
        "ActionId": 41,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 201,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '500702'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 42,
        "ActionId": 42,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Echo', 3: 'We often wait for the moment when a poem and a person meet. Sometimes a poem reminds you of someone; sometimes someone makes you remember a poem. The poems of the past are as countless as the stars...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 43,
        "ActionId": 43,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": "DialogDisable",
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Echo', 3: 'When that starlight from the past shines down on us, that\\'s when we truly understand poetry. Thank you for joining my poetry class. Today\\'s lesson is over.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 44,
        "ActionId": 44,
        "NextActionId": null,
