        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Together you set every desk and chair back in place. The moon is already above the treetops, its pale light pouring through the windows and resting where the afternoon sun once lay. The two of you can\\'t help but turn your eyes to the bright moon outside.'}"
    },
    {
